							<h3 class="mb-2 font-[var(--font-body)] text-[19px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--text-heading)]">Open the playground</h3>
							<p class="m-0 text-[15px] text-foreground">Write a slide, switch every palette, export a real PDF. In the browser, right now.</p>
						</a>
						<a
							href={url('getting-started/')}
							class="group block rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-[26px] text-card-foreground shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-lg"
						>
							<h3 class="mb-2 font-[var(--font-body)] text-[19px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--text-heading)]">Render your first deck</h3>
							<p class="m-0 text-[15px] text-foreground">Install the toolchain and produce a boardroom-grade PDF in a few minutes.</p>
						</a>
						<a
							href={SOURCE_DOC}
							class="group block rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-[26px] text-card-foreground shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-lg"
							rel="nofollow noopener"
							target="_blank"
						>
							<h3 class="mb-2 font-[var(--font-body)] text-[19px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--text-heading)]">Read the method ↗</h3>
							<p class="m-0 text-[15px] text-foreground">Every claim on this page, with its sources, its caveats, and the parts we could not fully verify.</p>
						</a>
					</div>
					<p class="mt-8 max-w-[62ch] text-[13px] leading-[1.6] text-muted-foreground">
						Method: we researched 18 tools in June 2026 and leaned on primary sources first, official docs and pricing
						pages, then recent reviews. These tools move fast, and some claims are contested — pricing and AI features
						most of all. Where we could not verify a number, we kept it qualitative. The full source ledger lives in
						the repo. Spot something out of date? Send a correction.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
